# CUET Medical Center Management System — Architecture & Implementation Plan

A Django + Django REST Framework web application for managing campus healthcare at CUET.  
**Backend only** — exposes a RESTful JSON API consumed by any frontend (or Django templates later).

---

## 1. Technology Stack

| Layer | Choice |
|---|---|
| Language | Python 3.12+ |
| Framework | Django 5.x |
| API Layer | Django REST Framework 3.15+ |
| Auth | `djangorestframework-simplejwt` (access + refresh tokens) |
| Database | SQLite (dev) / PostgreSQL (prod) |
| Filtering | `django-filter` |
| Docs | `drf-spectacular` (OpenAPI / Swagger UI) |
| CORS | `django-cors-headers` |
| AI Health Assistant | OpenAI-compatible API (optional, behind feature flag) |

