## 3. Data Models (ER Design)

### 3.1 `accounts.User` (Custom — extends `AbstractUser`)

| Field | Type | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| `email` | EmailField | **login field**, unique |
| `role` | CharField | choices: `student`, `doctor`, `admin` |
| `student_id` | CharField | nullable, only for students |
| `phone` | CharField | optional |
| `is_active` | BooleanField | default True |

> **USERNAME_FIELD = `email`**; students self-register, doctors are created by admin, admin via `createsuperuser`.

---

### 3.2 `records.MedicalRecord`

| Field | Type | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| `id` | AutoField | PK |
| `patient` | FK → User | student only |
| `doctor` | FK → User | doctor only |
| `diagnosis` | TextField | |
| `prescription` | TextField | |
| `notes` | TextField | optional |
| `created_at` | DateTimeField | auto |
| `updated_at` | DateTimeField | auto |

---

### 3.3 `roster.DoctorSchedule`

| Field | Type | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| `id` | AutoField | PK |
| `doctor` | FK → User | |
| `day_of_week` | CharField | choices: Mon–Sun |
| `start_time` | TimeField | |
| `end_time` | TimeField | |
| `is_available` | BooleanField | default True |

### 3.4 `roster.Ambulance`

| Field | Type | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| `id` | AutoField | PK |
| `vehicle_number` | CharField | unique |
| `driver_name` | CharField | |
| `driver_phone` | CharField | |
| `status` | CharField | choices: `available`, `busy`, `maintenance` |
| `updated_by` | FK → User | admin |
| `updated_at` | DateTimeField | auto |

---

### 3.5 `bloodbank.BloodDonor`

| Field | Type | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| `id` | AutoField | PK |
| `user` | OneToOne → User | student |
| `blood_group` | CharField | choices: A+, A−, B+, B−, O+, O−, AB+, AB− |
| `phone` | CharField | |
| `is_available` | BooleanField | default True |
| `last_donation_date` | DateField | nullable |

### 3.6 `bloodbank.BloodRequest`

| Field | Type | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| `id` | AutoField | PK |
| `requested_by` | FK → User | admin |
| `blood_group` | CharField | same choices |
| `units_needed` | IntegerField | |
| `urgency` | CharField | choices: `normal`, `urgent`, `critical` |
| `status` | CharField | choices: `open`, `fulfilled`, `cancelled` |
| `message` | TextField | optional |
| `created_at` | DateTimeField | auto |

---

### 3.7 `notifications.Notification`

| Field | Type | Notes |
|---|---|---|
| `id` | AutoField | PK |
| `title` | CharField | |
| `message` | TextField | |
| `target` | CharField | choices: `all`, `students`, `doctors` |
| `created_by` | FK → User | admin |
| `created_at` | DateTimeField | auto |

