## 4. API Endpoints

All endpoints prefixed with `/api/v1/`.

### 4.1 Auth (`/api/v1/auth/`)

| Method | Endpoint | Access | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| POST | `/register/` | Public | Student self-registration |
| POST | `/login/` | Public | JWT token obtain (email + password) |
| POST | `/token/refresh/` | Authenticated | Refresh access token |
| GET | `/me/` | Authenticated | Current user profile |
| PUT | `/me/` | Authenticated | Update own profile |

### 4.2 Medical Records (`/api/v1/records/`)

| Method | Endpoint | Access | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| GET | `/` | Doctor (own patients), Admin (all), Student (own) | List records |
| POST | `/` | Doctor | Create record |
| GET | `/{id}/` | Doctor/Admin/Student(own) | Record detail |
| PUT | `/{id}/` | Doctor (own records) | Update record |
| DELETE | `/{id}/` | Admin | Delete record |

### 4.3 Roster (`/api/v1/roster/`)

| Method | Endpoint | Access | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| GET | `/schedules/` | All authenticated | List doctor schedules |
| POST | `/schedules/` | Doctor (own), Admin | Create schedule |
| PUT | `/schedules/{id}/` | Doctor (own), Admin | Update schedule |
| DELETE | `/schedules/{id}/` | Admin | Delete schedule |
| GET | `/ambulances/` | All authenticated | List ambulances |
| POST | `/ambulances/` | Admin | Add ambulance |
| PUT | `/ambulances/{id}/` | Admin | Update status |
| DELETE | `/ambulances/{id}/` | Admin | Remove ambulance |

### 4.4 Blood Bank (`/api/v1/blood/`)

| Method | Endpoint | Access | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| GET | `/donors/` | Admin, Doctor | List donors (filterable by blood_group) |
| POST | `/donors/` | Student | Register as donor |
| PUT | `/donors/{id}/` | Student (own) | Update availability |
| GET | `/requests/` | Admin | List blood requests |
| POST | `/requests/` | Admin | Create blood request |
| PUT | `/requests/{id}/` | Admin | Update request status |

### 4.5 Notifications (`/api/v1/notifications/`)

| Method | Endpoint | Access | Description |
|---|---|---|---|
| GET | `/` | All authenticated | List notifications (filtered by target + role) |
| POST | `/` | Admin | Create notification |
| GET | `/{id}/` | All authenticated | Notification detail |
| DELETE | `/{id}/` | Admin | Delete notification |

